docs {
  # Get Chat Details
  
  Get details about a specific chat window.
  
  ## Path Parameters
  - `terminalId` (string): Terminal ID (format: tmux-{sessionName}:{windowIndex})
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "chat": {
      "id": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
      "terminalId": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
      "windowName": "chat-claude-auth-bug",
      "tool": "claude",
      "topic": "auth-bug",
      "sessionName": "mobile-project",
      "windowIndex": 1,
      "currentPath": "/path/to/project",
      "active": true,
      "type": "chat"
    }
  }
  ```
}
